    {
        quote: "Had an amazing time at The Taco Project in Tarrytown! Everything was so good — from the Palomas and Mojitos to the Spicy Mango and Passion Fruit Margaritas. We loved the Buffalo Wings, Tuna Tostadas, and Nachos. The tacos were the best — Birria, El Pastor, and Shrimp, full of flavor. Finished with Flan and one of the best Tres Leches ever. Big thanks to Julian for being so friendly and helping us with the menu!",
        author: "Anju Kapoor",
    },
    {
        quote: "The catering for our office lunch was phenomenal. Tacos remained fresh, hot, and the setup was seamless. The team loved the variety of salsas and the guacamole was a hit!",
        author: "Sarah Jenkins",
    },
    {
        quote: "We hired The Taco Project for our backyard summer party and it was the highlight of the season. The staff was professional and the food was authentic and delicious. Highly recommend the Birria tacos!",
        author: "Mike Ross",
    },
    {
        quote: "Absolute perfection. Ordered a taco bar for a birthday party and it couldn't have been easier. Great portions, fresh ingredients, and everyone went back for seconds.",
        author: "Elena Rodriguez",
    },
];
